{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/use-ffmpeg-to-extract-subtitles-from-videos","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9caef665-e6b6-59a6-96e1-4b0550e4813d","frontmatter":{"title":"使用ffmpeg提取视频中的字幕","hero":{"id":"5068f7d2-88e1-51de-b914-d8c8fd877837","childImageSharp":{"id":"1a664de1-c6e2-5584-b9c5-2929b902ec93","fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7699115044247788,"src":"/static/3b5ba6595bd14002bf043b863953d002/ee604/ffmpeg.png","srcSet":"/static/3b5ba6595bd14002bf043b863953d002/69585/ffmpeg.png 200w,\n/static/3b5ba6595bd14002bf043b863953d002/497c6/ffmpeg.png 400w,\n/static/3b5ba6595bd14002bf043b863953d002/ee604/ffmpeg.png 800w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}},"date":"2020-01-24","path":"post/use-ffmpeg-to-extract-subtitles-from-videos","tags":["字幕","工具"]},"html":"<p>使用下面这行代码可以提取视频中的「软字幕」。「软字幕」对应的是「硬字幕」，后者是像水印一样打在画面上的，前者是可以通过播放器控制是否显示的。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ffmpeg -i movie.mkv -map 0:s:0 subs.srt</code></pre></div>\n<p>以上代码假设了视频的名称为<code>movie.mkv</code>，其中</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>-i</code>代表「input」；</li>\n<li><code>-map</code>指出提取的是视频中的哪部分；</li>\n<li>后面跟着的<mark>第一个</mark><code>0</code>是指「第一个视频」（这里只有一个视频）；</li>\n<li><code>s</code>指的是「subtitles字幕」；</li>\n<li><mark>最后的</mark><code>0</code>指字幕中的第一个（因为视频可以含有多个字幕文件）；</li>\n<li>最后的<code>subs.srt</code>是指把提取出来的srt格式的字幕文件命名为「subs」。</li>\n</ul>"},"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"CY Is Here"}}},"pageContext":{"pathName":"post/use-ffmpeg-to-extract-subtitles-from-videos","prev":{"frontmatter":{"path":"post/how-to-do-feminist-media-analysis-star-trek-edition","tags":["女性主义","星际迷航","贝克德尔-华莱士测试","流行文化"],"title":"【译】如何对媒体做女性主义分析：《星际迷航》版"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"post/why-taste-metal","tags":["生活"],"title":"为什么吃东西会有金属味道"}}}}}